Package: OmniSciKit
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Clinical Statistical Toolkit
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Ablikim", "Ali", email = "medical_stat@163.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for clinical research and biostatistics.
    Integrates sample size calculation, statistical analysis, data visualization,
    power analysis, effect size calculation, clinical prediction model sample size,
    and clinical tools. Includes 8 real clinical datasets for demonstration and practice.
    Covers superiority, non-inferiority, and equivalence trial designs,
    survival analysis, regression models, and diagnostic test evaluation.
